<h1> Rules </h1>
<h3>Summary</h3>
<p>
You pick NFL teams <br>
You get points for crimes that the players on those teams commit <br>
</p>
<h3>Picking Teams</h3>
<p>
At the start of the season, you pick 3 different teams that will earn you points all season long <br>
Each week, you pick a bonus team. Crimes by players on the bonis team will earn you 3x points! <br>
</p>
<h3>Earning Points</h3>
<p>
Each crime committed will be awarded points depending on what occurred (see Scoring) <br>
Every game that a player is suspended for a crime is an additional point! <br>
Additionally, 5 points will be awarded for completing your teams quest <br>
</p>
<h3 style="color:red;">Countdown to Doomsday! - NEW for 2020 the Season</h3>
<p>
 Don't believe what you're hearing. There is no way for the NFL to contain the coronavirus! <br>
 When the season ends early (and it will) score big points for selecting the right day!
</p>

